Description: markdown-emdash
        ===============
        
        Extension for `python-markdown <https://python-markdown.github.io/>`__
        that replaces all triple dashes (``---``) with em-dashes (``&mdash;``).
        
        More information on `extensions
        here <https://python-markdown.github.io/extensions/>`__.
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        ::
        
            pip install markdown-emdash
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        .. code:: python
        
            markdown.markdown(some_text, extensions=[EmDashExtension()])
        
